* fibonacci.sno
* Bottleneck: deep recursion, function call/return overhead.
* FIB(18) = 2584, requires ~10,945 recursive SNOBOL4 function calls.
* Expected: 2584
    DEFINE('FIB(N)')                        :(FIB_END)
FIB     FIB = LT(N,2) N                    :S(RETURN)
    FIB = FIB(N - 1) + FIB(N - 2)     :(RETURN)
FIB_END
    OUTPUT = FIB(18)
END
